spec_data.Name: mariadb-java-client
spec_data.Description:
MariaDB Connector/J is a Type 4 JDBC driver, also known as the Direct to
Database Pure Java Driver. It was developed specifically as a lightweight
JDBC connector for use with MySQL and MariaDB database servers.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 29 Aug 2017 08:12:01 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Connects applications developed in Java to MariaDB and MySQL databases
